JS语法检查

FunkyRicky    2015 - 2022

JS语法检查

FunkyRicky 2022/2/11 WEB前端Webpack

# 依赖插件安装

yarn add eslint-loader eslint eslint-config-airbnb-base eslint-plugin-import -D
1

# 使用eslint-loader的时候报错

TypeError: Cannot read property ‘getFormatter’ of undefined

解决: eslint版本从8降为7.32.0
1
2
3
yarn add eslint@7.x -D
1

# eslint配置

然后在项目根目录下面新建文件 .eslintrc.js

module.exports = {
  extends: 'airbnb-base',
};
1
2
3

# webpack.config.js配置修改

/* eslint-disable new-cap */
const { resolve } = require('path')
const HtmlWebpackPlugin = require('html-webpack-plugin')

module.exports = {
    mode: 'development',
    entry: './src/index.js',
    output: {
        filename: 'build.js',
        path: resolve(__dirname, 'dist'),
        publicPath: './',
    },
    module: {
        rules: [
            {
              test: /\.js$/i,
              loader: 'eslint-loader',
              // 不检查第三方的打包好的源码
              exclude: /node_modules/,
              options: {
                // 自动修复eslint的错误
                fix: true,
              }
            }
        ]
    },
    plugins: [
        new HtmlWebpackPlugin({
            template: './template/index.html',
            filename:'index.html',
        }),
    ],
}

src/index.js

var foo = 'bar'
1

npx webpack
1
